OL,3,CActor James Tolkan of 'Top Gun' and
OL,4,C'Back to the Future' fame dies at 94
OL,6,FActor James Tolkan, known for his
OL,7,Froles as a cigar-chomping naval
OL,8,Fcommander in "Top Gun" and a gruff
OL,9,Fhigh school administrator in "Back to
OL,10,Fthe Future," has died at the age of 94.
OL,12,FTolkan died Thursday in Lake Placid,
OL,13,FNew York, where he lived, his booking
OL,14,Fagent, John Alcantar, said Saturday.
OL,16,FA brief obituary published on the
OL,17,F"Back to the Future" website said
OL,18,FTolkan died "peacefully," but no cause
OL,19,Fof death was given.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
