OL,3,CActor James Tolkan of 'Top Gun' and
OL,4,C'Back to the Future' fame dies at 94
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn "Back to the Future," Tolkan
OL,12,Fportrayed the bow tie-wearing vice
OL,13,Fprincipal Gerald Strickland, who
OL,14,Feyeballed students for trouble in the
OL,15,Fhalls of the fictitious Hill Valley
OL,16,FHigh School ` in particular Marty
OL,17,FMcFly, played by Michael J. Fox.
OL,19,FTolkan also appeared in "Top Gun" as
OL,20,Fcommanding officer Tom "Stinger"
OL,21,FJardian.
