OL,3,CActor James Tolkan of 'Top Gun' and
OL,4,C'Back to the Future' fame dies at 94
OL,6,FBorn in Calumet, Michigan, Tolkan
OL,7,Fgraduated from high school in Arizona
OL,8,Fand served in the Navy during the
OL,9,FKorean War.
OL,11,FHe eventually made his way to New
OL,12,FYork, where he spent a quarter century
OL,13,Facting in theater roles. He was a
OL,14,Fmember of the original ensemble cast
OL,15,Fof "Glengarry Glen Ross."
OL,17,FTolkan's wife, Parmelee Welles, said
OL,18,Fin a statement that her husband also
OL,19,Fwas an avid art collector and adored
OL,20,Fanimals.
